: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>RTHK應該趁熱係《傑出華人系列》，《我們的科學家》表揚呢隻一下啦！！！</strong></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a6732f81f26021dbf12a788ea7804f54472dcee5","tid":569120,"uid":71315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"好明顯係美國人黎，同中國無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb017ed65ccaeec7284e7be737515037f5087b70","tid":569120,"uid":35814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a6732f81f26021dbf12a788ea7804f54472dcee5","tid":569120,"uid":71315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"好明顯係美國人黎，同中國無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"乜唔係首先係中國人咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188925c18291fb94eb57fb53fff08dbebd96691c","tid":569120,"uid":162424,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T17:00:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf007e6a909f499da3205e1074de8f03bc1b0848","tid":569120,"uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.mp.sohu.com/upload/20170729/e2a74bbf11804643ac891aba34317cf4_th.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.mp.sohu.com%2Fupload%2F20170729%2Fe2a74bbf11804643ac891aba34317cf4_th.png&h=3851afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">席同志<br />\n不要放弃<br />\n请记住<br />\n在你身後<br />\n有一个强大的祖国！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2017/08/22/0/0b28ef591d1e2f02641a19a4d5095235.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F0%2F0b28ef591d1e2f02641a19a4d5095235.jpg&h=80a3e485&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f7d8cd87baf69455259879c9f21c8e83d05330f","tid":569120,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1488776b5a4a7383fd5e96e6033aecfbd9af87a7","tid":569120,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:39:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T21:26:59.000Z","msg":"中共中宣部明令嘉勉五毛dewi👿<br />\n<br />\n中國仲慘黨 <br />\n<br />\n遭殃宣傳部 <br />\n<br />\n輿情信息局 <br />\n<br />\n網絡監控辨公室 <br />\n<br />\n通告<br />\n<br />\n中宣發2018年(167)號文件 <br />\n<br />\n查有忠誠五毛dewi👿不負黨疼國愛，日日為本黨領導人含撚，致患口腔癌，更天天努力在連登開膠post，被連登網民屌到屎忽開花，痔瘡爆裂，搞到一褲都係。<br />\n<br />\n本辨除明令頒發「網絡評論員勞動模範」證書予該五毛外，更通令香港樁亂辨體侐該員愛黨致殘，特許給予「免為本黨領導人含撚假期」，為時一月，亦特準增加出帖工資1毛，該員昇級為6毛，是本黨前所未有慷慨之舉。<br />\n<br />\n本黨興廢，在輿情一戰，各員一層，奮勵努力，定點連登，屢敗屢戰，屎忽開花，在所不計。<br />\n<br />\n抄本送呈: <br />\n<br />\n香港樁亂辨文教宣傳部 <br />\n<br />\n香港特衰正苦內地含撚事務局局長洩得權"},{"pid":"a8d67cefb5fcf65eb6ef5fd5a225880a10a888e0","tid":569120,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T22:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0241b28832a320c9209212c250574c9536c63ad3","tid":569120,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb017ed65ccaeec7284e7be737515037f5087b70","tid":569120,"uid":35814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a6732f81f26021dbf12a788ea7804f54472dcee5","tid":569120,"uid":71315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"好明顯係美國人黎，同中國無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"乜唔係首先係中國人咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"衰野就唔係，好野先係"}]}